Features:

* Spreadsheet support
All different kind of spreadsheet formats supported

* Two step approach
First step converts XLS into dbdir.tab, tables.tab, units.tab.
Second step creates SQL command from the 3 tab files.

* Perl based
Perl based and portable.

* Tablespace support (to be implemented)
Tablespace names can be defined in Spreadsheet

* No static template files required

* No hard coded stuff
Exception: The spreadsheet is parsed positional.

* Removal of LONG
Replaced by CLOB/TEXT

* Postgres support (to be implemented)

* Additional indexes (to be implemented)
Unique, composite and unique composite indices supported

* Consistency check
Spreadsheet is checked for consistency

* CI/CD support
Can be used by Jenkins

* Meaningful error messages


